{"tid":1059071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"體驗中国特色婚禮  坐轎過橋女子被從3公呎高摔到地上 (有片)","createTime":"2019-03-13T01:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T01:59:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"098a59b4031d98003a001cbf8a499e8ff5691dd3","tid":1059071,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T01:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190313/640_454ca4870930ecd6e15d28cba354a44f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190313%2F640_454ca4870930ecd6e15d28cba354a44f.jpg&h=1ea07b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國安徽銅陵的一個風景區，上周五（8日）為了重現古代的婚禮習俗，找來一名女子扮演新娘坐花轎。沒想到女子坐著花轎過橋時，因為傾斜角度過大，轎內椅子突然脫落。她放聲尖叫後，整個人從3公尺高處栽到地上，跌個狗吃屎。<br />\n <br />\n影片曝光後，當地村主任坦承，「很像」有女子被風景區人員摔到地上。至於傷勢，村主任含糊地說：「肯定有點小傷，但是還好啦，就送到醫院了嘛」。被問到是不是轎子沒做防護（固定）措施，村主任則不斷閃躲，僅稱：「應該還好」、「我也不知道」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190313/1532253/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190313%2F1532253%2F&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BeoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=43960395\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190313%2F1532253%2F&h=2ff485c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190313/1532253/</a>"}]}